description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for midwives with enthusiasm for delivering high quality, women centered care, to join our community and maternity in-patients team. Successful candidates will need excellent communication and a broad clinical knowledge base.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We take pride in delivering responsive care to women and families. We serve a diverse population, covering a wide and varied landscape.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer flexible working and an attractive salary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are currently employed by the Trust and want to join the Northern Healthcare Trust Staff Bank then please contact the staffbank team at ndht.staffbank@nhs.net as you do not need to apply for this vacancy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviews will be completed via Skype, Zoom or telephone during the current pandemic climate.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
